# Redflag Website Scanner

This is a simple website scanning tool built with Python that allows you to quickly check the security of your website. It scans for common vulnerabilities such as SQL injections, cross-site scripting (XSS), and file inclusion vulnerabilities.

## Requirements

To run this script, you'll need to have Python 3 installed on your computer. You can download it from the [official Python website](https://www.python.org/downloads/).

You will also need to install the following Python libraries:

pip install requests
pip install bs4
pip install lxml

You can install them by running the following command:

pip install -r requirements.txt


